{"type": "article", "id": 3937, "title": "从《纽约时报》风尚版百年看社会变迁", "description": "Best On The Web 是一个推荐性栏目，每个工作日我们会从互联网世界中找出最好看的内容，希望这个栏目让我们始终与阅读、知识和美好在一起。", "date": "2014-11-28T08:08:22Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 594, "name": "纽约时报"}, {"id": 4684, "name": "风尚版"}, {"id": 4685, "name": "女权运动"}, {"id": 1225, "name": "美国"}, {"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}, {"id": 165, "name": "时装"}], "category": 12, "author": 13, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606042202073xuUQfhDSOV2P70G.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<strong>The Awl</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://www.theawl.com/2014/11/the-history-of-the-new-york-times-styles-section?src=longreads&amp;mc_cid=81e4fbd0f2&amp;mc_eid=22fb1bd789\" target=\"_blank\">Bonfire of the inanities</a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t作家和历史学家 Jacqui Shine<a href=\"http://www.theawl.com/2014/11/the-history-of-the-new-york-times-styles-section?src=longreads&amp;mc_cid=81e4fbd0f2&amp;mc_eid=22fb1bd789\" target=\"_blank\"> <strong>为 Awl 撰写的长文</strong></a>展现了过去 100 年来《纽约时报》风尚版（Style Section）的演变历程。阅读这篇 12000 个单词的文章就像是看另一部《Sex and the City》，你会发现比起单独看某一期的风尚版获得了更多时尚、文化和纽约的知识。所谓的「风尚版」一度让一些人觉得有些愚蠢而肤浅，但事实上它比我们想象中的要更为复杂和丰富。<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这其间见证了很多历史事件的发生，包括</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">女性为「同工同酬」的抗争。而那些如今看上去异常蹩脚的审美，也有更为实用的考虑，比如法兰绒上衣和军靴，只是为了更好地对抗太平洋西北部那种变化无常的气候。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604220205oQEgUMu2fPDyYahv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.521875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604220206fBCLnWrK3SDR0lqQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042202062uCn5AwbN7180KEi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}